{"tid":659762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：單車手　粵普雙語演繹雙面人","createTime":"2018-05-10T06:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T13:39:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c39c33c9a551789be601e303897779a74ac167e","tid":659762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180510/20386426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20386426&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FETA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=850c39c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20386426&h=b112ed65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180510/20386426</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月10日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：單車手　粵普雙語演繹雙面人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180510/large/a1406a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180510%2Flarge%2Fa1406a.gif&h=cd746cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n俗語有云「見人講人話，見鬼講鬼話」。近日fb流傳一條片，片段見到有單車選手因單車爆胎相當勞氣，拍片人走近以普通話訪問對方，單車手先以一連串廣東話粗口投訴，但迅速變臉以普通話大讚附近環境好，爆胎只因不小心，完美示範何謂雙面人。<br />\n<br />\n影片見到兩名單車手疑似修理爆胎單車，拍片人以普通話走近問佢覺得條路點，雙面人爆seed：「XX佢呀，呢啲咁嘅X路，又濕，路又爛，下次畀都唔X嚟呀。」<br />\n<br />\n拍片人以普通話追問可否用普通話講，雙面人即變臉大讚環境好、路又漂亮，「我超喜歡這裏，以後我每年都會來參加這裏的活動的。」拍片人追問佢點解會爆胎？」<br />\n<br />\n雙面人又用廣東話鬧：「你問咁多托X呀？」拍片人以普通話速回：「你剛剛說甚麼？」雙面人再變臉話係自己不小心，不是路滑問題。<br />\n<br />\n短片幾日已有過千shares和likes，有網民笑指，「廣東話=真情流露嘅說話；普通話=耍官腔全是廢話」。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：腰已拗　食環vs街斗上的女檔販<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866164e30edc9ce3d5936a7fea2d00ac06603252","tid":659762,"uid":143582,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SgTCiTeebOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSgTCiTeebOc&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FETA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e5e439eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SgTCiTeebOc</a>"},{"pid":"2c0af956f78dc9a34111cdd28376c02557e5d1b9","tid":659762,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"866164e30edc9ce3d5936a7fea2d00ac06603252","tid":659762,"uid":143582,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SgTCiTeebOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSgTCiTeebOc&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FETA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e5e439eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SgTCiTeebOc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70faa5878cf548ed0fff9ca441c4ad3b1cc4c6cb","tid":659762,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces